dans l'histoire

645
01:01:40,200 --> 01:01:41,240
et saute le reste.

646
01:01:43,320 --> 01:01:44,240
Réfléchis !

647
01:01:44,830 --> 01:01:45,830
D'accord.

648
01:01:49,540 --> 01:01:50,370
Donc,

649
01:01:50,660 --> 01:01:52,920
